						<span class="authorlink"><a href='http://trilema.com/2017/the-masters-textbook-why-do-girls-seek-you-out?b=as%20they%20best&amp;e=ht%29%2C#select' class='url'>The Master's Textbook - Why do girls seek you out ? on Trilema - A blog by Mircea Popescu.</a></span>&nbsp;(via Pingback)						<span class=""></span>
